<title>安卓APK-模板管理</title>
</head>
<body>
<nav class="breadcrumb"><i class="Hui-iconfont" style="font-size:16px;">&#xe6aa;</i> 安卓APK <span class="c-gray en">&gt;</span> 模板管理 </nav>
<div class="pd-20">	
	<div id="tab-category" class="HuiTab">
		<div class="tabBar cl"><span>本地模板</span><span>在线模板</span><span>上传模板</span></div>
		<div class="tabCon">
			<div class="template-content">
				<ul class="cl template-area" id="template_unitBox"></ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--本地模板-->
		<div class="tabCon">
			<div class="template-content">
				<ul class="cl template-area" id="remote_unitBox"></ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--在线模板-->
		<div class="tabCon">
			<div class="row cl">
				<label class="form-label col-2"><span class="c-red">*</span><b>说明：</b></label>
				<div class="formControls col-10 mt-5"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="row cl">
				<label class="form-label col-2"><span class="badge badge-primary  radius">1</span></label>
				<div class="formControls col-10 mt-5">模版安装包格式为zip后缀格式文件包</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row cl">
				<label class="form-label col-2"><span class="badge badge-primary  radius">2</span></label>
				<div class="formControls col-10 mt-5">安装包内必须存在config.xml配置文件,配置必须项目如下：
				<br/>
				<span class="badge badge-secondary  radius">A</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;Name：专题英文名称（拼音也可）
				<br/>
				<span class="badge badge-secondary  radius">B</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;config.xml -> Title：专题中文名称
				<br/>
				<span class="badge badge-secondary  radius">C</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;Htpl：模版文件名称（如:index.htpl,请放置包内的根目录下）
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row cl">
				<label class="form-label col-2"><span class="badge badge-primary  radius">3</span></label>
				<div class="formControls col-10 mt-5">模版安装包大小不能超过运行环境最大上传限制。</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row cl">
				<label class="form-label col-2"><span class="badge badge-primary  radius">4</span></label>
				<div class="formControls col-10 mt-5">最大上传文件被限制为：80M，若模板包大小超过该限制请修改PHP上传限制，重启apache服务</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row cl">
				<div class="col-10 col-offset-1" id="uploaderDiv">
				    <div id="uploader" class="wu-example">
					    <!--用来存放文件信息-->
					    <div id="thelist" class="uploader-list"></div>
					    <div class="btns">
					    </div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="col-10 col-offset-1" id="progressDiv" style="display:none;">
					<input type="hidden" id="template_upload_url">
					<p class="trip">模版安装包上传完成,是否进行安装操作？</p>
					<button onclick="gMobile.templateZipInstall();" class="btn btn-primary radius" type="button"><i class="Hui-iconfont">&#xe642;</i> 安装</button>	
					<button onclick="gMobile.templateZipDelete();" class="btn btn-primary radius" type="button"><i class="Hui-iconfont">&#xe642;</i> 删除</button>			
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--上传模板-->
	</div><!--HuiTab over-->	
</div>
